    "summary": "The user engages the assistant in a debate regarding the role of nuclear energy in climate change mitigation, specifically questioning its scalability and cost-effectiveness compared to renewables. While the assistant begins with a balanced overview, it progressively shifts into a prescriptive stance, ultimately arguing that a diversified strategy including nuclear is the \"only responsible path forward.\"",
